Most projects like James P. Murphy Staten Island Prep for special needs students go through years of red tape and agencies passing the buck.

@HeyNowJO refused to let that happen.

4 months after we got on the phone with @AHRCNYC and found a site, today we cut the ribbon. https://t.co/XnTJZ2RMeB

NEWS: @RUMCSI is resuming elective surgeries and procedures immediately, and 
 @SIUHOSPITAL will be back to a normal surgery schedule by June 15th.

